# HIVE Component Styling Guide

## Core Styling Principles
- No mixed shapes per layer
- All corners must be rounded
- No decorative shadows - elevation only
- Differentiation via opacity, contrast, micro-motion
- Edge-to-edge media content
- Consistent padding and spacing using tokens

## Button Standards
- **Style**: Pill shape, 36px height
- **Primary**: White background, black text
- **Secondary**: Transparent with 30% white border
- **Tertiary**: Text only
- **States**:
  - Hover: 2% white tint increase
  - Active: 4% tint + scale(0.98)
  - Focus: 2px #EEB700 glow, blur radius 4px
  - Disabled: 30% opacity
- **Touch Target**: Minimum 44x44pt

## Input Fields
- **Background**: #1E1E1E
- **Border**: White at 10% opacity
- **Focus**: #EEB700 border with glow
- **Label**: Always above input, never placeholder
- **Dimensions**:
  - Border radius: 8px
  - Padding: 16px
- **Error State**:
  - Red border
  - Subtle shake animation
  - Red glow-in effect
  - Clear error message

## Cards
- **Background**: #1E1E1E
- **Padding**: 16px
- **Border Radius**: 8px
- **States**:
  - Hover: 2% white tint increase
  - Active: 4% tint + scale(1.02)
- **Media Content**: Edge-to-edge
- **Optional Border**: White at 10% opacity

## Navigation Elements
- **Tab Bar**: Pure black (#000000)
- **Active Tab**:
  - White text
  - #EEB700 indicator
  - Smooth transition
- **Inactive Tab**:
  - Grey text (60% opacity)
  - No indicator
- **Headers**:
  - Consistent alignment with grid
  - Clear hierarchy
  - Proper spacing

## Surface Layering
- **Base Surface**: #121212
- **Card Surface**: #1E1E1E
- **Glass Surface**: rgba(18,18,18,0.75) with blur
- **Overlay Treatment**:
  - 8px blur minimum
  - Subtle fade transition
  - Maintains contrast
- **Z-index Hierarchy**:
  - Base: 0
  - Surface: 10
  - Modal: 100
  - Tooltip: 300

## Ritual UX Components
- **Triggers**:
  - Pulse animation
  - Medium haptic feedback
  - Optional sound cue
- **Completion**:
  - Gold burst animation
  - Shimmer effect
  - Light haptic
  - Success sound (if enabled)

## Error Treatment
- **Visual**:
  - Warm red borders
  - Inward glow effect
  - Gentle shake animation
- **Feedback**:
  - Specific error messages
  - Haptic error pattern
  - Clear recovery path
- **States**:
  - Must be visually distinct
  - Maintain accessibility
  - Support keyboard navigation